{"results":[{"aya":"043","id":4889,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"你们中不信道的人们比这等人还优秀呢！还是天经中有关于你们的赦条呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"044","id":4890,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"难道他们说：我们是一个常胜的团体。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"045","id":4891,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"那个团体将败北，他们将转背。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"046","id":4892,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"不然，复活时是他们的约期；复活时是更艰难的，是更辛苦的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"047","id":4893,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"犯罪者的确在迷误和烈火中。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"048","id":4894,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"他们匍匐着被拖入火狱之日，将对他们说：你们尝试火狱的烧灼吧！","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"049","id":4895,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"我确已依定量而创造万物，","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":8,"previousPage":"/zh/s054-6.json","nextPage":"/zh/s054-8.json"}}